es were allocated through the qualification process, in which athletes won quota places for their respective nation.<ref name=\"FILA\" />\n\n==Qualification summary==\n{{Wrestling2012Olympics}}\n\n==Qualification timeline==\n\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! width=300|Event !! width=200|Date !! width=230|Venue\n|-\n| [[2011 World Wrestling Championships|2011 World Championships]]<ref name=\"World 2011\">{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924012946/http://www.fila-official.com/images/FILA/resultats/2011/results_09_istanbul.pdf|title=World Championship Senior \u2013 Results|publisher=[[International Federation of Associated Wrestling Styles|FILA]]|accessdate=17 March 2012}}</ref> || September 12\u201318, 2011 || {{flagicon|TUR}} [[Istanbul]], [[Turkey]]\n|-\n| [[2012 African & Oceania Wrestling Olympic Qualification Tournament|African & Oceania Qualification Tournament]]<ref name=\"Africa\">{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329130346/www.fila-official.com/images/FILA/news/resultats_temporaires/results_marra_qualifs.pdf|title=Qualified countries for London\u2019s Olympic Games at the African and Oceania OG qualifying tournament \u2013 2nd phase |publisher=[[International Federation of Associated Wrestling Styles|FILA]]|accessdate=18 March 2012}}</ref> || March 16\u201318, 2012 || {{flagicon|MAR}} [[Marrakesh]], [[Morocco]]\n|-\n| Pan American Qualification Tournament<ref name=\"Pan-Am\">{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924012954/www.fila-official.com/images/FILA/resultats/2012/results_03_kissimmee.pdf|title=Pan-American OG Qualifying Tournament \u2013 Results|publisher=[[International Federation of Associated Wrestling Styles|FILA]]|accessdate=30 March 2012}}</ref> || March 23\u201325, 2012 || {{flagicon|USA}} [[Kissimmee, Florida|Kissimmee]], [[United States]]\n|-\n| Asian Qualification Tournament<ref name=\"Asia\">{{cite web|url=http://www.fila-official.com/images/FILA/resultats/2012/results_03_astana.pdf|title=Asian OG Qualifyi