|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| [[2012 African & Oceania Wrestling Olympic Qualification Tournament#48 kg|African & Oceania Qualification Tournament]] || align=\"center\"|2 || {{flagIOCathlete|[[Isabelle Sambou]]|SEN|2012 Summer}}<br />{{flagIOCathlete|[[Maroi Mezien]]|TUN|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| Pan American Qualification Tournament || align=\"center\"|2 || {{flagIOCathlete|[[Clarissa Chun]]|USA|2012 Summer}}<br />{{flagIOCathlete|[[Patricia Berm\u00fadez]]|ARG|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| Asian Qualification Tournament || align=\"center\"|2 || {{flagIOCathlete|[[Kim Hyung-joo]]|KOR|2012 Summer}}<br />{{flagIOCathlete|[[Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb L\u1ee5a]]|VIE|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| European Qualification Tournament || align=\"center\"|2 || {{flagIOCathlete|[[Iwona Matkowska]]|POL|2012 Summer}}<br />{{flagIOCathlete|[[Alexandra Engelhardt]]|GER|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| 1st World Qualification Tournament ||  align=\"center\"|2 || {{flagIOCathlete|[[Davaas\u00fckhiin Otgontsetseg]]|MGL|2012 Summer}}<br />{{flagIOCathlete|[[Vanesa Kaladzinskaya]]|BLR|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| 2nd World Qualification Tournament ||  align=\"center\"|2 || {{flagIOCathlete|[[Iryna Merleni]]|UKR|2012 Summer}}<br />{{flagIOCathlete|[[Mayelis Carip\u00e1]]|VEN|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| Invitational / Host Country || align=\"center\"|1 || {{flagIOCathlete|[[Tanoh Benie]]|CIV|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n! Total !! 19 !!\n|}\n\n===55 kg===\n{|class = \"wikitable\"\n|-\n! width=300|Competition !! width=80|Places !! width=300|Qualified wrestlers\n|-\n| [[2011 World Wrestling Championships \u2013 Women's freestyle 55 kg|2011 World Championships]] || align=\"center\"|6 ||{{flagIOCathlete|[[Saori Yoshida]]|JPN|2012 Summer}}<br />{{flagIOCathlete|[[Tonya Verbeek]]|CAN|2012 Summer}}<br />{{flagIOCathlete|[[Tetyana Lazareva]]|UKR|2012 Summer}}<br />{{flagIOCathlete|[[Ida-Theres Karlsson-Nerell|Ida-Theres Nerell]]|SWE|2012 Summer}}<br />{{flagIOCathlete|[[Maria Gurova]]|RUS|2012 Summer}}<br />{{flagIOCathlete|[[Helen Maroulis]]|USA|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| 