elly Glover]] (MP for [[Saint Boniface (electoral district)|Saint Boniface]], 2008-2015 and [[Minister of Canadian Heritage]] and Official Languages 2013-2015) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/PeterMacKay/status/1234675326170517509|title=Proud to have the support of my friend and former cabinet colleague Shelly Glover|first=Peter|last=MacKay|date=2 March 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Laurie Hawn]] (MP for [[Edmonton Centre]], 2006-2015)\n*[[Ryan Leef]] (MP for [[Yukon (electoral district)|Yukon]], 2011-2015) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/PeterMacKay/status/1242869446261252106|title=Thank you @RyanLeefMP.|first=Peter|last=MacKay|date=25 March 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Wladyslaw Lizon]] (MP for [[Mississauga East\u2014Cooksville]], 2011\u20132015) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/wladyslawlizon/status/1224145461214400513|title=I am very happy and excited to support and campaign for my friend @PeterMacKay for the leader of @CPC_HQ and the next Prime Minister|first=Wladyslaw|last=Lizon|date=2 February 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Costas Menegakis]] (MP for [[Richmond Hill (electoral district)|Richmond Hill]], 2011\u20132015) <ref>[https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2752645011486482&set=a.136198029797873&type=3&theater ]{{dead link|date=February 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Ted Menzies]] (MP for [[Macleod (electoral district)|Macleod]], 2004\u20132013)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/TedMenzies/status/1220507938332110848?s=20|title=I am proud to support my long-time friend and former colleague @petermackay to become the next leader of the @CPC_HQ.|last=Menzies|first=Ted|date=23 January 2020|website=@TedMenzies\n|language=en|access-date=23 January 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Rob Nicholson]] (MP for [[Niagara Falls (electoral district)|Niagara Falls]], 2004\u20132019)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/PeterMacKay/status/1232397328616652800?s=20|title=Thank you for your support Rob, it was great to see you in Niagara Falls last weekend.pic.twitter.com/QCNR0XINZJ|first=Peter|last=MacKay|dat